== Nyakatsi ==[[File:Rwanda cultural house (NYAKATSI).jpg|thumb|Rwanda cultural house (NYAKATSI)]]
mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] ndetse no mubindi bihugu byinshi bya [[Afurika|Africa]] hagiye hagaragara izu

zubatswe mubyatsi cyangwa mubirere nibiti zizwi kwi zina rya nyakatsi<ref>https://www.google.com/search?sxsrf=ALeKk02wSEsH3m4xXDt8RbLHBfYXh8fnQA:1629797994385&source=univ&tbm=isch&q=nyakatsi&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwi2z4rUrsnyAhXDgf0HHQAICKYQjJkEegQIBRAC&biw=1207&bih=579</ref>

ni inzu zaturwagamo nabakene cyane cyane mubihugu byabo

== umwihariko ==
nyakatsi n [[Inzu ndangamurage y'Umwami|inzu]] zikozwe mu byatsi zirangwa cyane no gukonja

kubazirimo imbere kuko wasanganga nta muriro ubamo ahubwo

ugasanga bacanyemo inkwi kugirango habone ndetse bakabikora no

muburyo bwo kota kugirango bashyuhe<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/26773</ref> 

== Iterambere ==
muri ibibihe nko mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] no mubindi bihugu birimo gutera imbere 

bigize umugabane wa [[Afurika]] ntago hakigaragaramo [[Inzu ndangamurage y'Umwami|inzu]] zituwemo na

abaturage<ref>https://www.radiyoyacuvoa.com/a/demolition-of-grass-huts-in-rwanda-111764104/1266256.html</ref> zizwi nka [[Inzu ndangamurage y'Umwami|nyakatsi]]

== Ubukungu ==
kugeza ubu inzu za nyakatsi ahantu zisigaye mu Rwanda

cgangwa muri Afurika ntago zituwemo na Abaturage ahubwo zahinduwe

inzu [[Inzu ndangamurage y'Umwami|ndangamurage]] zibyo bihugu<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/bakuwe-muri-nyakatsi-batuzwa-heza-ngo-amaherezo-bazatunga-n-imodoka</ref>

== Ubukerarugendo ==[[File:Inside of Rwanda cultural house.jpg|thumb|Inside of Rwanda cultural house]]
Inzu za nyakatsi zahinduwe amateka mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] kuko nta muturage ukizituyemo

ahubwo zabaye izaba mukerarugendo<ref>https://globalpressjournal.com/africa/rwanda/common-housing-structure-to-be-razed-in-favor-of-modern-villages-in-rwandan-district/</ref> kuko zirzsurwa cyane kandi zibarizwa cyane mu ma [[Hotel Rwanda|Hotel]]

